verses.text: Unto \w the|strong="H0413"\w* end, \w for|strong="H0413"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* winepresses, \w a|strong="H0413"\w* \w psalm|strong="H4210"\w* \w for|strong="H0413"\w* \w Asaph|strong="H0623"\w* \w himself|strong="H0413"\w*.
Rejoice \w to|strong="H3478"\w* God \w our|strong="H3478"\w* helper: sing aloud \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3427"\w* God \w of|strong="H3427"\w* Jacob.

Take \w a|strong="H6440"\w* psalm, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* bring hither \w the|strong="H0853"\w* timbrel: \w the|strong="H0853"\w* pleasant psaltery \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H0853"\w* harp.

Blow up \w the|strong="H6440"\w* trumpet \w on|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* new moon, \w on|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* noted day \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w your|strong="H7725"\w* solemnity.

\w For|strong="H6635"\w* \w it|strong="H5704"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H5704"\w* commandment \w in|strong="H0430"\w* \w Israel|strong="H5971"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H5704"\w* judgment \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w of|strong="H0430"\w* Jacob.

He ordained \w it|strong="H0398"\w* \w for|strong="H3899"\w* \w a|strong="H0398"\w* testimony \w in|strong="H3899"\w* Joseph, when he came out \w of|strong="H3899"\w* \w the|strong="H0398"\w* land \w of|strong="H3899"\w* Egypt: he heard \w a|strong="H0398"\w* tongue \w which|strong="H3899"\w* he knew \w not|strong="H0398"\w*.

\w He|strong="H7760"\w* removed \w his|strong="H7760"\w* back from \w the|strong="H7760"\w* burdens: \w his|strong="H7760"\w* hands \w had|strong="H7760"\w* \w served|strong="H7760"\w* \w in|strong="H7760"\w* baskets.

Thou calledst upon \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w in|strong="H0430"\w* affliction, \w and|strong="H0430"\w* I \w delivered|strong="H3467"\w* thee: I heard thee \w in|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* secret place \w of|strong="H0430"\w* tempest: I proved thee \w at|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* waters \w of|strong="H0430"\w* contradiction.

Hear, O \w my|strong="H5265"\w* \w people|strong="H1471"\w*, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w I|strong="H4714"\w* \w will|strong="H1471"\w* testify \w to|strong="H4714"\w* thee: O Israel, if thou wilt hearken \w to|strong="H4714"\w* me,
There \w shall|strong="H0776"\w* \w be|strong="H0776"\w* no new god \w in|strong="H0776"\w* thee: neither shalt thou adore \w a|strong="H0776"\w* strange god.

\w For|strong="H2022"\w* \w I|strong="H6738"\w* am \w the|strong="H3680"\w* Lord thy \w God|strong="H0410"\w*, \w who|strong="H0410"\w* brought thee out \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H3680"\w* land \w of|strong="H2022"\w* Egypt: open thy mouth wide, \w and|strong="H2022"\w* \w I|strong="H6738"\w* \w will|strong="H2022"\w* fill \w it|strong="H3680"\w*.
\w But|strong="H0413"\w* \w my|strong="H7971"\w* people heard not \w my|strong="H7971"\w* voice: \w and|strong="H7971"\w* Israel hearkened not \w to|strong="H0413"\w* \w me|strong="H0413"\w*.

\w So|strong="H5674"\w* \w I|strong="H4100"\w* let \w them|strong="H1870"\w* \w go|strong="H5674"\w* according \w to|strong="H1870"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* desires \w of|strong="H1870"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* heart: \w they|strong="H4100"\w* \w shall|strong="H4100"\w* \w walk|strong="H1870"\w* \w in|strong="H1870"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* own inventions.
If \w my|strong="H7462"\w* people \w had|strong="H7704"\w* heard me: if Israel \w had|strong="H7704"\w* walked \w in|strong="H7704"\w* \w my|strong="H7462"\w* ways:

\w I|strong="H7200"\w* should soon \w have|strong="H7200"\w* humbled \w their|strong="H7725"\w* enemies, \w and|strong="H0430"\w* laid \w my|strong="H7200"\w* hand \w on|strong="H7200"\w* \w them|strong="H7725"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* troubled \w them|strong="H7725"\w*.

\w The|strong="H0834"\w* enemies \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3225"\w* \w have|strong="H0834"\w* lied \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w*: \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w their|strong="H5921"\w* time \w shall|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* ever.

\w And|strong="H6440"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* fed \w them|strong="H6440"\w* \w with|strong="H8313"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* fat \w of|strong="H6440"\w* wheat, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* filled \w them|strong="H6440"\w* \w with|strong="H8313"\w* honey \w out|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* rock.
